---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Global Servicing Platform">
  <h1>Global Servicing Platform</h1>

  <p style="font-size: 22px; margin-top: 16px;">
    Improving a large-scale servicing platform through clearer workflows, stronger UX foundations, and more consistent product thinking.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);"></div>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Context</h2>
    <p>
      The platform supported complex servicing operations across multiple regions, but suffered from fragmented experiences, inconsistent patterns, and operational inefficiencies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Challenge</h2>
    <p>
      How might we improve usability and consistency across a large, distributed platform while supporting diverse operational workflows?
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Introduced stronger UX foundations, aligned patterns across the system, and improved workflows through clearer structure and design consistency.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Outcome</h2>
    <p>
      Improved usability, reduced friction across workflows, and created a more scalable foundation for continued platform evolution.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>